hopobject.body: Pleased to meet you 40 mg nexium vs prilosec Politics forced the House to drag its feet on the farm bill this summer. Internal GOP squabbles over how much money should be spent on the country's food assistance programs, forced the House to separate the agricultural portion of the bill from the nutrition title. As it stands now, the House has passed an agriculture bill, but has not voted on a bill to reform food stamps.
